Changelog

Key -
* = Changed
- = Removed
n = New feature
b = Bugfix

1.1.0 - Recode - 31st March 2009
* Refactored/rewrote almost all the code to be easier to work with. This introduced new bugs which got fixed so not listing individual bug fixes this release.
* Made coding/naming conventions far more consistant.
* Added a lot of comments.
n New tag system.
n Comment field on add/edit image and gallery now can be expanded if needed.
n New upload method allows more than one image file at a time, plus is dynamic, no more page refreshes so it can provide a recent history.
n Upgrade.php.

1.0.0 - Initial Release - 28th Jan 2009